When we say “The Chef’s Challenge,” we mean it! ⏲️

This season of Table Scraps raises the stakes, so it’s only fitting that we brought in expert judges to take on the challenge! 🏆

Meet Gino, Lanette, and Antonia—Bakersfield’s very own food and wine legends. With deep roots in the restaurant industry, they know a great dish when they taste one. And what better place to bring them in than Luigi’s (@Luigisbakersfield)—a Bakersfield institution for 115 years and a true cornerstone of the community. 🍝

Oh, and fun fact? They also happen to be John Sacco’s in-laws! We love our Luigi’s family!

Will anyone WOW the judges? Find out March 14th! ♻️
